The '''Autem family''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] family in the final [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. Members included:
*[[Sagoro Autem's grandfather]]
*[[Sagoro Autem's father]]
*[[Sagoro Autem]]
*[[Venco Autem]]
*[[Sula Autem]]
*[[Reymet Autem]]
*[[Lissa Autem]]

Both Sagoro's and Sula's side of the family were descended from lines consisting of generations of [[Senate Guard/Legends|Senate Guards]].

